result.name: Kim Mun Dong Korean Restaurant

reviews.text: Local Korean food in Hong Kong, nothing special

this Korean restaurant has a spacious setting equipped with Korean barbecue griller. Its windows are facing an open area outside mtr station giving a good street view.  I had ordered a Korean stone pot beef rice as lunch and it was quite worthy for hkd45 in comparison with ordinary fast food shop in hk.
Great value … Great food
Reasonable portion and price, good.
Quite clean and tidy but too less choises for the food at the buffet .

reviews.text: 牛肋骨很好吃！店員服務勤快，而且貼心的主動地替我們換板及調節火候，夠細心！
訂左十三位，結果比得八位點坐十三人。早到左問侍應到時係咪一定有位。待應回應係一定有。無語了了。
食物停加，伙記服務殷切，咁嘅價錢OK啦。
差，燒肉冇肉汁，入口乾，湯粉湯底味差
